title: #92Noon Leber/Bercich/Zimmer Presser/Wobby
description: PA breaks down the Vikings/Jaguar game from the weekend. Ben Leber and Pete Bercich weigh in on the new helmet rule. "It's an art, not a science." Says Pete. Our long term relationship with the Vikings and the politics of dating. PA takes your calls. Mike Zimmer's press conference live from TCO, talking rules and penalties. Wobby in studio.
